    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this exemplary vehicle, maintained to an uncompromising standard of excellence. This unit represents the pinnacle of its class, preserved in a pristine state that demands the attention of the discerning collector. Every facet of this motorcar\u2014from the flawless exterior contours to the immaculate, factory-fresh interior\u2014testifies to its meticulous provenance and limited use. This is an investment-grade opportunity for those who refuse to settle for anything less than mechanical and aesthetic perfection.",
      "price": 48500.0,
